.TH SPACEGL_DIAG 1 "2026-04-19" "SpaceGL @VERSION@" "SpaceGL Manual"
.SH NAME
spacegl_diag \- SpaceGL real-time diagnostic scanner
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B spacegl_diag
.I PID
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B spacegl_diag
is an ncurses-based real-time diagnostic tool for the SpaceGL engine.
Given the PID of a running
.BR spacegl_server (1)
process, it attaches to the server's shared memory segment and displays
live diagnostic data including entity states, network statistics, SHM
layout, and system health indicators.
.PP
.B spacegl_diag
is typically launched via
.BR spacegl_diag.sh (1),
which handles server PID detection and opens a dedicated xterm session
with optimized terminal geometry.
.SH ARGUMENTS
.TP
.I PID
The process ID of the running
.B spacegl_server
instance to inspect.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I /usr/bin/spacegl_diag
Diagnostic executable.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR spacegl_diag.sh (1),
.BR spacegl_hud (1),
.BR spacegl_server (1)
.SH AUTHOR
Nicola Taibi
